<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        @page {
            size: A4;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        body {
            font-family: "PingFang TC", "Microsoft JhengHei", sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            min-height: 297mm;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        /* Main Image Section */
        .main-image-container {
            width: 100%;
            height: 400px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background-color: #eee;
            position: relative;
        }
        .main-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        .image-counter {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 15px;
            right: 20px;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }

        /* Header Section */
        .header {
            padding: 25px 30px 15px 30px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 20pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .tag-container {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .tag {
            background: #f2f2f2;
            color: #666;
            padding: 3px 10px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-size: 9pt;
            margin-right: 6px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        /* Price Highlight Section */
        .price-section {
            padding: 0 30px 20px 30px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        }
        .price-box {
            background: #fff9f5;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #ffe4d1;
        }
        .total-price {
            color: #fa350f;
            font-size: 32pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: block;
        }
        .unit-price-highlight {
            background: #fa350f;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 2px 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 16pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .sub-price {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 11pt;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }

        /* Info Grid */
        .info-grid {
            display: table;
            width: calc(100% - 60px);
            margin: 20px 30px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        }
        .info-item {
            display: table-cell;
            width: 25%;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .info-label {
            color: #999;
            font-size: 10pt;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .info-value {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 13pt;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Sections */
        .section {
            padding: 25px 30px;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-size: 15pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-left: 4px solid #fa350f;
            padding-left: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #1a1a1a;
        }
        
        .detail-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        .detail-table td {
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f8f8f8;
            font-size: 11pt;
        }
        .detail-label {
            width: 100px;
            color: #999;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* Features */
        .feature-item {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .feature-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 12pt;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .feature-icon {
            color: #fa350f;
            margin-right: 8px;
        }
        .feature-desc {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 11pt;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        /* CTA Footer */
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 8px solid #f5f5f5;
        }
        .btn-call {
            background: #fa350f;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px 80px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(250, 53, 15, 0.2);
        }
        .link-text {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 15px;
            color: #007bff;
            font-size: 9pt;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Image Section -->
        <div class="main-image-container">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hao713949/Dagui-Section/main/%E5%A4%A7%E8%B2%B416.png" class="main-image" alt="土地現況">
            <div class="image-counter">1 / 1</div>
        </div>

        <div class="header">
            <div class="tag-container">
                <span class="tag">住宅用地</span>
                <span class="tag">都市計畫內</span>
                <span class="tag">景觀視野</span>
                <span class="tag">大面寬</span>
            </div>
            <div class="title">【北屯北坑特二】景觀住宅用地 ‧ 地面平整臨6米路</div>
        </div>

        <div class="price-section">
            <div class="price-box">
                <span class="total-price">5,149 <small style="font-size: 18pt;">萬元</small></span>
                <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
                    <span class="unit-price-highlight">單價：16 萬 / 坪</span>
                    <span class="sub-price">| 參考自備款 5成 (約2,575萬)</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">土地面積</div>
                <div class="info-value">321.8 坪</div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">土地種類</div>
                <div class="info-value">住宅/農地</div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">使用分區</div>
                <div class="info-value">住宅區</div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">臨路路寬</div>
                <div class="info-value">6 米</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">基礎資訊</div>
            <table class="detail-table">
                <tr>
                    <td class="detail-label">物件編號</td>
                    <td class="detail-value">S19332828</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="detail-label">地段</td>
                    <td class="detail-value">台中市北屯區大貴段</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="detail-label">現況</td>
                    <td class="detail-value">空地 (地面已平整)</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="detail-label">建蔽率</td>
                    <td class="detail-value">10%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="detail-label">面寬深度</td>
                    <td class="detail-value">面寬 24.4m x 深度 15.9m</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">物件特色</div>
            
            <div class="feature-item">
                <div class="feature-title"><span class="feature-icon">💎</span> 地形優勢：方正開發容易</div>
                <div class="feature-desc">具備大面寬格局，利於建築設計規劃，室內採光與景觀視野極佳。</div>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
                <div class="feature-title"><span class="feature-icon">🚛</span> 交通機能：臨6米路活巷</div>
                <div class="feature-desc">路況優良，工程機具或大型車輛進出便利，減少建築成本支出。</div>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
                <div class="feature-title"><span class="feature-icon">🏫</span> 優質學區：美式生活圈</div>
                <div class="feature-desc">鄰近華盛頓中學、台中美國學校，高資產族群首選區段，增值潛力高。</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <a href="https://land.591.com.tw/sale/19332828" class="btn-call">立即聯繫 預約看地</a>
            <a href="https://land.591.com.tw/sale/19332828" class="link-text">點擊查看 591 原始物件詳情</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
